*cogl-1.22.0-r1 (23 Jan 2016)

  23 Jan 2016; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> +cogl-1.22.0-r1.ebuild,
  +files/cogl-1.22.0-fglrx.patch, +files/cogl-1.22.0-initial-output.patch,
  +files/cogl-1.22.0-wait-flip.patch:
  Apply upstream fixes, also fix cogl not working at all with fglrx drivers,
  we need to apply the fix conditionally until someone figures out how to
  properly check for fglrx presence for the patch (#567168, upstream bug
  #756306, thanks to Olcay for reporting and testing this).

  Package-Manager: portage-2.2.26

